text: Antonio de Almeida is the name of: * Antonio de Almeida (conductor) (1928–1997), French conductor * António José de Almeida (1866–1929), sixth president of Portugal *Antonio de Almeida e Costa (1932–2010), Portuguese naval officer and politician *António de Almeida Santos (1926–2016), Portuguese politician
title: Antonio de Almeida
